title: The Favorites - Guest Tiki Barber
itunes:title: The Favorites - Guest Tiki Barber
description:
One of the greatest New York Giants of all-time, friend of the podcast Tiki Barber joins Action Network hosts Chad Millman and Simon Hunter to talk about about Russell Wilson, the value of teamwork, his reality show athletic prowess, a new partnership with Knights of Degen and so much more. #Herd
